        "delineation": "Chapter",
        "number": 25,
        "summary": "In Mount Zion the Lord will prepare a gospel feast of rich food\u2014He will swallow up death in victory\u2014It will be said, Lo, this is our God.",
        "chapterAugmentations": [],
        "verses": [
            {
                "text": "O Lord, thou art my God; I will exalt thee, I will praise thy name; for thou hast done wonderful things; thy counsels of old are faithfulness and truth.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 13,
